{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act34side_level_act34side_05_end","storyGroup":"act34side","storySort":11,"storyDependence":"act34side_level_act34side_05_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BP-5","storyName":"不治的命运","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"西昆妲审讯袭击研究所的深海教徒。深海猎人在手术完成后，离开城市。博士从乌尔比安口中得知当年斩杀伊莎玛拉行动的更多真相。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act34side/level_act34side_05_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act34side_05","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":9,"next":11,"characters":["受伤的“研究员”","西昆妲","斯卡蒂","歌蕾蒂娅","幽灵鲨","？？？","艾丽妮","乌尔比安"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a3/Avg_bg_51_g11_aegirroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":7},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":8,"musicid":0},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":9},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1392_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":11},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"海巡队。你是来审问我的？","id":13,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"“审问”，哈，我从没想过这个词居然会和自己有关。","id":14,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"你在侵入研究所的时候就应该想到了。","id":16,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"在那之前呢？你我之间究竟有什么区别？","id":18,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"为什么你在这里“审问”，而我在这里“受审”？","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"我有时候会觉得我们的手段太温和了。","id":21,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"听伊比利亚的使节说，他们会在审问阶段就应用刑罚。","id":22,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"......","id":24,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"如果没有更多废话了，交代你的身份。","id":26,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"我先前负责培育行道珊瑚。","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"作案动机？","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"你有仔细观察过路边的行道珊瑚吗，海巡队？","id":32,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"我们希望每一条街道的每一株行道珊瑚，都呈现出不同的形态、色泽，甚至承载不同的功能。","id":33,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"斗智场东侧的那一株，物流缆线从它满是空洞的身躯间穿行，在缆线微光的映照下，一只只珊瑚虫反射出点点明光......","id":34,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"就像是一片小小的星云。","id":35,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"还有港口枢纽外围——","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"就在刚刚，我仔细观察了不止一株行道珊瑚，在你们先前的试验田。","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"一位无辜的数据员就在那里死去。","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"......","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"她的理想，她的执念，她所喜爱的那些藻类......与你所描述的行道珊瑚一样美。","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"但你们谋害了她。","id":44,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"你问得很对。那你与她之间究竟有什么区别？","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"为什么你能活着，而她必须死去？","id":46,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"因为她发现......","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"发现了什么？怎么不说了？","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"还是说，我应该把这个问题拿去问卡西娅？","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"你......","id":53,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"深海教会对航道计划动了什么手脚？","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"你们集中攻击的是信标，还是武器？","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"说。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"唉，深海教会，深海教徒。","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"我还是很不习惯被这么称呼，好陌生的名字。真不是你们海巡队为了方便抓人才起的这些名字吗？","id":61,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"......","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"所谓教会、教徒，它的神圣性在哪里？","id":65,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"我甚至没在崇拜什么虚无缥缈的存在，我只是认同卡西娅的看法。","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"从弥漫在阿戈尔的绝望当中，她看到了这个国家的脆弱性。","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"人们太过看重事物的价值，却又不肯承认这些价值是多么脆弱而多变，他们变成了某种既定价值的忠实信徒。","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"可现在，这种价值正在崩塌。在阿戈尔完全陷入绝望之前，总有人得敲响警——","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":70},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"all","id":71},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":72},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":73},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","focus":"r","id":74},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"*阿戈尔感叹词*！你在套我的话。","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"受伤的“研究员”","text":"我不会再说一个字了。你要是不耐烦，大可以解析我的脑波，又不费什么事——","id":77,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_1392_1$1.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":78},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"提问是对你身为人的最后一点尊重，渣滓！","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"你可以认为自己是无辜的，也可以认为自己的所作所为不属于阴谋。但你会一点不落地吐出这些信息。","id":81,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"现在，说。","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/af/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":83},{"type":"dialog","id":84},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"charslot","id":86},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":87},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_bg_51_g9_shipport.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":88},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":89},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$rebel_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act11d0d0/m_bat_rebel_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":90,"musicid":1},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":91},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","duration":"1","id":92},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"char_263_skadi#3","duration":"1","id":93},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":94},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"r","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"二队长。","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"斯卡蒂，离我们出发的时间很近了。","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"r","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我知道情况很紧急。","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"前线的军力只能勉强与海嗣维持均势，整整两支舰队完全覆灭的恶果到现在完全显现了出来。","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"按照他们刚刚传回的消息，第八、第十军团几次尝试变阵都以失败告终，他们陷入了苦战。","id":103,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","focus":"l","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"如果无法将信标投放到巢穴内的指定位置，继续僵持......意味着航道计划的失败。","id":105,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"char_263_skadi#9","focus":"r","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我明白。","id":107,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_char_263_skadi_9.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"军团的舰队即将不计代价地向海嗣发起全线进攻，吸引海嗣的注意力，至于我们——","id":109,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"r","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我们会切入战场的死角，深入巢穴，投放信标。","id":111,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"嗯。斯卡蒂，你觉得自己的状态怎么样？","id":113,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"char_263_skadi#5","focus":"r","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"至少刚才我睡得很好。自那场战役以来，我还是第一次体验无梦的睡眠。","id":115,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_char_263_skadi_5.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"现在城内的局势越发动荡......你知道博士去哪了吗？","id":117,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"r","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"（摇头）","id":119,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"二队长，我知道你提博士是想说什么。你想让我去维持秩序，保护博士......总之，你想让我继续留在城里。","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"坦白地说，我在犹豫。","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"清扫海洋里的渣滓是深海猎人的责任，但我也需要为你们的安全负责。","id":123,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"斯卡蒂，回到海洋后，伊莎玛拉是否有醒转的迹象？","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"r","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"如果它在，那它很安静。","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"如果它说话，那我会让它闭嘴。","id":127,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"二队长，我找你其实有话要说。","id":128,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"char_263_skadi#8","focus":"r","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我们之前做事从来不像现在这样谨小慎微。我们有一套应对这种情况的做法。","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_char_263_skadi_8.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"如果那些深海教徒的神，那些渣滓口中的“伊莎玛拉”真的存在在我的身体里，一旦我失控，那么你当场处决我，很简单。","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_char_263_skadi_8.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我的心脏就在这里，你不会失手。","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_char_263_skadi_8.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","focus":"l","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"斯卡蒂——","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"char_263_skadi#8","focus":"r","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"还没完，二队长。","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_char_263_skadi_8.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"如果你，或者鲨鱼，在战斗中比我先受到了那些渣滓的影响，我也不会手下留情。","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_char_263_skadi_8.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......","id":139,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#3","focus":"l","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"斯卡蒂，我刚刚是想说，大战在即，没什么能比这样一番话更让人欣慰了。","id":141,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"我们走。","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":143},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":144},{"type":"charslot","id":145},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":146},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1","id":147},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":148},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"......","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"劳伦缇娜小姐。","id":152},{"type":"dialog","id":153},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":154},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":155},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":156},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1","focus":"r","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"小鸟，去掉那让人难过的后缀吧，我们之间原来这么生分吗？","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"......劳伦缇娜。","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"来到阿戈尔的城市这么久，我们竟然才第一次见面，真令人难过。","id":162,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"我一直想带我们勇敢的战士见识海洋深处真正的狩猎。偏偏这次我们要去的巢穴太远、太深，没法带上你。","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"不，就算不是这样，我现在也应该留在弥利亚留姆。","id":165,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"哦？","id":167,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"这段时间，城里发生了一些事。","id":169,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"我第一次穿戴深潜装置进入海洋，立刻就被海流冲得东倒西歪......我必须承认，这样的我无法成为助力，只会成为拖累。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1","focus":"r","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"倒也不必这么妄自菲薄。第一次总是艰难的。","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"总之，相比巢穴，我在城市里能做的事更多。","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"等你们完成任务，阿戈尔的武器系统开始净空这片海域时，我还需要尽快回到卡门阁下身边，应对海面上的变化。","id":175,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"啊，原来你的意思是，我们还会再多分开一段时间。","id":177,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/86/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"没错。","id":179,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"本该给你们带些饯别的礼物，可来到弥利亚留姆之前，我没料到会有这种情况，没能准备什么......","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"别担心，我们还会再见的。","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"虽然这次不必把呛得半死的你从海里抱上来，但我觉得这次大战后的重逢会以另一种方式刻骨铭心。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"咳！......斯卡蒂她们来了！","id":186,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"劳伦缇娜，你多小心。","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":188},{"type":"charslot","id":189},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":190},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","duration":"1","id":191},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"char_263_skadi#3","duration":"1","id":192},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":193},{"type":"charslot","id":194},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"你们聊完了？","id":196,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"嗯。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"出发吧，猎人们。","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":200},{"type":"dialog","id":201},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":202},{"type":"charslot","id":203},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":204},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_bg_51_g5_aegirstreet_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":205},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":206},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":207},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":208},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1","duration":"1","id":209},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":210},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$suspenseful_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_suspenseful_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":211,"musicid":2},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"博士。","id":212},{"type":"dialog","id":213},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":214},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"216","text":"看来你已经得到了你想要的证据。"}},"values":[],"id":215},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":216,"end":218},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#8$1","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"嗯，你的帮助很大。","id":218,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":219},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":220},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"222","text":"那么，结果是？"},"2":{"id":"222","text":"不打算将发现同步给我吗？"}},"values":[],"id":221},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":222,"end":228},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我先前提到，尚在城内的信标与已经投放进海嗣巢穴的信标之间，存在异常的信息交互。","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"现在来看，大部分操作都是在C-22研究所，也就是我们刚刚潜入的地方完成的。","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我并不完全了解信标系统与第Ⅳ级武器的原理，但从这些信息交互的内容依然能模糊地推断出——","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"信标与武器的联动关系被改变了。","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"如我所想，航道计划从高层被渗透了。","id":228,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":229},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":230},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"232","text":"“如我所想”。"},"2":{"id":"232","text":"你从一开始就对航道计划抱有这样的怀疑？"}},"values":[],"id":231},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":232,"end":235},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"没错。","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"早在航道计划诞生之前，我就已经对阿戈尔产生了怀疑。","id":235,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":236},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":237},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"239","text":"这种怀疑从何而来？"}},"values":[],"id":238},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":239,"end":241},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......那场决定性的战役。","id":241,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":242},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":243},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"245","text":"本该是你向“初生”挥出致命一击。"}},"values":[],"id":244},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":245},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"247","text":"你却在关键时刻与队伍失去了联系。"}},"values":[],"id":246},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":247},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"249","text":"将斩杀“初生”的重负留给了斯卡蒂。"}},"values":[],"id":248},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":249,"end":252},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......你已经知道了。","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"斯卡蒂比我预想中还要信任你。","id":252,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":253},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":254},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"256","text":"根据她的描述，不难推测当时的情形。"},"2":{"id":"256","text":"斯卡蒂其实并不清楚发生了什么。"}},"values":[],"id":255},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":256,"end":263},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#4$1","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我的失职是出于一瞬间的分神。","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"在最靠近伊莎玛拉核心器官的那个洞窟，或者腔室，我发现了某样本不应存在的东西。","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"粗糙的肉质层，浑浊的黏液，我原本以为那只是它身体的某一处结节，直到我看清周边的刻度和纹路......","id":260},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"那是一个，锈蚀的水脉仪。","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......来自阿戈尔。几百年前的款式，现在只存在于博物馆中。","id":263,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":264},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":265},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"267","text":"几百年前？"}},"values":[],"id":266},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":267,"end":272},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"根据那个水脉仪的异化情况判断，它至少已经在伊莎玛拉体内留存了两百年。","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"但当初我得到的说法是，在我们之前，阿戈尔从未有人接触过“初生”的本体。","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"即是说，早在海嗣这种生物进入阿戈尔的视野之前，就已经有阿戈尔人与“初生”有过接触，而阿戈尔对此一无所知。","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"阿戈尔平静水面下的暗流，比所有人想象的都更加汹涌。","id":272,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":273},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":274},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"276","text":"你拿到证据的同时，我也发现了异样。"}},"values":[],"id":275},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":276},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"278","text":"猎人们苏醒之后立刻离开了，很急。"}},"values":[],"id":277},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":278,"end":281},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"猎人们被用来打破前线的僵局。","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"可以想象她们被委派了什么任务——绕过战线，直捣巢穴，投放信标。","id":281,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":282},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":283},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"285","text":"从辅助作战到被迫成为战术核心，太快了。"}},"values":[],"id":284},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":285,"end":287},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......","id":287,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":288},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":289},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"291","text":"此外，那位顾问表现得比猎人们还要焦急。"}},"values":[],"id":290},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":291},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"293","text":"猎人们苏醒后，他第一时间离开了研究所。"}},"values":[],"id":292},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":293,"end":299},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"布兰都斯。","id":295},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"那恐怕我们也必须尽快行动了。","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"如果信标与武器的联动关系遭人篡改，那么我应该去的地方只有一处——航道计划的核心场所，信标发射井。","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"而你......","id":299,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":300},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":301},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"303","text":"我会去见那个给猎人们下令的人。"}},"values":[],"id":302},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":303},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"305","text":"克莱门莎......执政官。"}},"values":[],"id":304},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":305,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":306},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":307},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":308},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":309},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":310},{"type":"image","id":311},{"type":"charslot","id":312}],"characters":["受伤的“研究员”","西昆妲","斯卡蒂","歌蕾蒂娅","幽灵鲨","？？？","艾丽妮","乌尔比安"]}